Name: Sei_Seqweaver
model_architecture:
IsoAbundanceModel(
  (IsoGNNModel1): GNN_Block(
    (conv1): GATv2Conv(23596, 512, heads=2)
    (bn1): BatchNorm1d(512, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (conv2): GATv2Conv(512, 512, heads=1)
    (bn2): BatchNorm1d(512, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (dropout): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
  )
  (IsoGNNModel2): GNN_Block(
    (conv1): GATv2Conv(512, 256, heads=2)
    (bn1): BatchNorm1d(256, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (conv2): GATv2Conv(256, 256, heads=1)
    (bn2): BatchNorm1d(256, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (dropout): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
  )
  (IsoGNNModel3): GNN_Block(
    (conv1): GATv2Conv(256, 128, heads=2)
    (bn1): BatchNorm1d(128, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (conv2): GATv2Conv(128, 128, heads=1)
    (bn2): BatchNorm1d(128, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (dropout): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
  )
  (linear1): Linear(in_features=23596, out_features=512, bias=True)
  (linear2): Linear(in_features=512, out_features=256, bias=True)
  (linear3): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=128, bias=True)
  (layernorm1): LayerNorm((512,), eps=1e-05, elementwise_affine=True)
  (layernorm2): LayerNorm((256,), eps=1e-05, elementwise_affine=True)
  (layernorm3): LayerNorm((128,), eps=1e-05, elementwise_affine=True)
  (dropout): Dropout(p=0.3, inplace=False)
  (head): Sequential(
    (0): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
    (1): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=128, bias=True)
    (2): ReLU()
    (3): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
    (4): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=30, bias=True)
  )
)
